{"id": "25634", "post": "<div class=\"post-25634 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-editorial tag-black-friday\" id=\"post-25634\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/top-ten-lowendbox-black-friday-cyber-monday-offers/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Top Ten LowEndBox Black Friday/Cyber Monday Offers</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/black-friday/\" rel=\"tag\">black friday</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> December 2, 2020 @ 4:00 am, by raindog308</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/lowendbox_300_bf_cm.png.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-25635 alignright litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/lowendbox_300_bf_cm.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" align=\"right\" hspace=\"20\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/lowendbox_300_bf_cm.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/lowendbox_300_bf_cm-150x150.png.webp 150w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/lowendbox_300_bf_cm.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/lowendbox_300_bf_cm-150x150.png.webp 150w\" data-was-processed=\"true\">Usually we try to get 3-4 offers per week posted on LowEndBox.&nbsp; Over the annual Black Friday/Cyber Monday event, we get flooded with offers from providers and we\u2019ve had over two dozen posted in the span of a few days.</p><p>And what terrific deals we\u2019ve seen!&nbsp; A big <strong>thank you</strong> to providers for participating on Black Friday/Cyber Monday.</p><p>It\u2019s tough to pick out just ten great offers \u2013 and of course, depending on your needs, any one of the offers could be your personal best.&nbsp; But ask I look across them, here are my picks, in no particular order:</p><ul><li>How could I not include <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/black-friday-hyperexpert-blows-the-doors-out-with-a-1gb-vps-for-1-year/\">Hyper Expert</a>\u2018s 1GB VPs for $1/year?&nbsp; What a door buster!</li><li><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/racknerd-brings-a-true-black-friday-offer-kvm-vps-in-9-locations-from-8-89-year-including-amd-ryzen-nvme-windows-vps/\">RackNerd</a>\u2018s huge spread of offers starting at $15.25/year for 1GB was awesome.&nbsp; I remember when 128MB for $15/year was a popular price point years ago \u2013 looks like we might be getting towards a new price point.</li><li><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/alphavpss-black-friday-offer-1gb-ryzen-vps-for-e15-year-in-bulgaria-or-los-angeles/\">AlphaVPS</a> offer 1GB for \u20ac15/year in LA or Bulgaria</li><li><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/cheap-windows-vps-best-offer-ever-54-yr-4gb-kvm-or-99-yr-8gb-kvm-vps-over-50-off/\">Cheap Windows VPS</a> offered a 4GB/60GB Windows VPS for $54/year which is amazing.</li><li>Some great shared offers including <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/limitless-hosting-black-friday-special-includes-3-year-shared-hosting-plus-vps-reseller-deals/\">Limitless</a>\u2018s $3/year deal</li><li>And speaking of shared, I\u2019ll also nominate <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/cybermonday-usa-cpanel-shared-hosting-for-4-25-year-from-teradelta-or-7-25-year-in-singapore/\">TeraDelta</a>\u2018s $4.25/year US and $7.25/year Singapore offer</li><li>You can never have enough storage and getting 8TB for $20/month is eye-popping \u2013 thanks, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/lions-mammoths-and-black-friday-offers-oh-my-servarica-is-here-4gb-for-10-mo-in-canada/\">ServaRICA</a></li><li><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/knownhost-has-some-awesome-dedi-offers-for-you-32gb-16-core-e5-only-20-83-mo-on-annual/\">KnownHost</a> had powerful dedis for $24.50/mo or $20.83/mo on annual contract</li><li>And if you need a ton of bandwidth, it was hard to resist <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/servermania-offers-big-managed-dedis-with-100tb-of-bandwidth-starting-at-99-mo/\">ServerMania</a>\u2018s 100TB offer</li><li><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/quadranet-exclusive-black-friday-dedi-offers-in-los-angeles/\">QuadraNet</a> rounds out the list with dedis starting at $39/mo with 30TB of bandwidth</li></ul><p>Again, thanks to all providers and congratulations to all our readers who got in on these great deals!</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Ftop-ten-lowendbox-black-friday-cyber-monday-offers%2F&amp;t=Top%20Ten%20LowEndBox%20Black%20Friday%2FCyber%20Monday%20Offers\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Top%20Ten%20LowEndBox%20Black%20Friday%2FCyber%20Monday%20Offers&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Ftop-ten-lowendbox-black-friday-cyber-monday-offers%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dp